address2: 25th Floor Cheung Sha Wan 538 Castle Peak Road
longBusinessSummary: Virtual Mind Holding Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the design, manufacturing, and trading of apparel in the People's Republic of China, the United States, and Hong Kong. It also offers designing, marketing, and advertising services; money lending services, which include loans to individual consumers and small businesses; sells gaming and animated characters related products; provides toys, garment, software technical advisory, and promoting services; and develops games and software; offers literature, graphic, and marketing design services; household products; and artwork design services. The company was formerly known as CEFC Hong Kong Financial Investment Company Limited and changed its name to Virtual Mind Holding Company Limited. Virtual Mind Holding Company Limited was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
